Deckers Outdoor Corp Overview



Website:

www.uggaustralia.com

Locations:


                                                             Goleta, CA 

                                                

Employees:
180




Founded:
N/A
CEO:
Angel Martinez
Industry:

Footwear



Revenue:
$208,343,390





                                            Based at 495 S Fairview Ave # A, Goleta, CA, footwear company Deckers Outdoor Corp has a lot to offer. It pulls in a yearly revenue of $208.3 million and employs 180 people. Recognized for its specialized appeal, Deckers Outdoor Corp has gained quite a popularity within the industry. Angel Martinez heads the company currently as CEO.
                                        









